setting up mysql
imagine your settings are:
/etc/zac.conf :
---
DBHOST: localhost
DBUSER: fai
DBPASSWORD: r4e3w2q1
DBNAME: fai


use the mysql cli..

create database fai;
grant all on fai.* to user fai identified by 'r4e3w2q1';


